<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Book a Visit — Sharp As Services</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --black: #0e0e0d;
    --off-white: #f5f2eb;
    --steel: #8a8a82;
    --gold: #b8933e;
    --gold-light: #d4a94e;
  }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--off-white);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 6vw;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 79px,
        rgba(184,147,62,0.05) 80px
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 7vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--off-white);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: rgba(245,242,235,0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .tel-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--off-white);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold);
    padding-bottom: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .tel-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  .tel-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--steel);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .back-link {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--steel);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(138,138,130,0.3);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover { color: var(--off-white); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">Sharp As Services</p>
    <h1>Online booking<br><em>coming soon.</em></h1>
    <p>In the meantime, just give us a call or send a text and we'll get you sorted.</p>
    <a href="tel:0220962925" class="tel-link">022 096 2925</a>
    <p class="tel-label">Call or text to book</p>
    <a href="index.html" class="back-link">← Back to site</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
